Package com.intellij.openapi.util

Class Disposer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intellij.openapi.util.Disposer

  • public final class Disposer
extends java.lang.Object
    Manages a parent-child relation of chained objects requiring cleanup.

    A root node can be created via newDisposable() to which children are attached via subsequent calls to register(Disposable, Disposable). Invoking dispose(Disposable) will process all its registered children's Disposable.dispose() method.

    See Also:
